{"tid":2280731,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[開關鋪路] 11．13起中國以外地區抵港者只可酒店檢疫","createTime":"2020-11-10T16:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T16:24:43.000Z","uid":354275,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a394ddaeb6d293c55dd0fd15dccba2413a047d0","tid":2280731,"uid":354275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"鑑於全球新型冠狀病毒疫情發展，港府公布，就《預防及控制疾病（規管跨境交通工具及到港者）規例》（第599H章）下的指明刊憲，抵港者若在登機日或14日內曾在中國以外的地區（不包括已指明的極高風險地區）停留，必須提供在香港酒店預訂房間的中文或英文確認書，其租住期間為抵港當日起計不少於14日，措施將於11月13日生效，直至另行通知，意味海外抵港者只可在酒店檢疫，不可家居檢疫。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201103/s00001/1604392601107/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-11-13%E8%B5%B7%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AA%E5%8F%AF%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB-%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E5%88%97%E6%A5%B5%E9%AB%98%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201103%2Fs00001%2F1604392601107%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-11-13%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E5%259C%259F%25E8%2580%25B3%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%2588%2597%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258D%2580&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Imvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=6a0f3e0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201103%2Fs00001%2F1604392601107%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-11-13%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25